data.description: A lovely country home on a peaceful dead-end road with a large yard. Sit on the front or back porch with your morning coffee and enjoy the bird songs, and maybe even catch sight of deer! Close enough for local shopping, 20 minutes to Bossier and Shreveport. Large living room and family rooms with wood-burning fireplace. Metal roof replaced and large back porch added in 2020. Large workshop or can be used as garage in back with ample parking for barbeques and family gatherings.
